{"tid":1465720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〈計中計〉唔好諗中計，乜野都有好處壞處","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:25:29.000Z","uid":156914,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f00c8245ef4a04ebf41c44a6e1d2d6e5ff53ffb4","tid":1465720,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"當你成日諗中計，你就真係中左對家計<br />\n<br />\n佢無方法從外圍擊敗你，咪從內圍瓦解你，令你覺得中計，你就會疑神疑鬼，之後不安不信任嘅氣氛就會擴大，到最後就會處處受束縛，乜都做唔到，所以有無計都好，對家最想你成日諗係咪中計<br />\n<br />\n其實每個有爭議嘅行為都必然有好處有壞處，如果已經做左，咪無限放大啲好處，盡量掩蓋啲壞處，甚至乎忽視啲壞處，如果下下都要完美，所有人都高興先行動，你永遠無法前進<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不談中計，協力突顯每個行動嘅好處"},{"pid":"f85b97dfb54ee95465ace4ab660d3375c435aa55","tid":1465720,"uid":156914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"a8208becbd6b31769be2dc17900659cec8798eb8","tid":1465720,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"e8601a35620bec564c37086000e4126ce75807fa","tid":1465720,"uid":267942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"D 鬼易捉到離奇，目的製造混亂？"},{"pid":"b16515f17c4d4a1d0d8146e4a865b2bd8831a5d2","tid":1465720,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"拒絕火鳳中計黨帶風向"},{"pid":"7f3c37052ae83218fb39ed4ec83acc98f5a9c84b","tid":1465720,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"721 811 無忘受傷被捕手足"},{"pid":"740c084d4203f9e627b98c395a4724bce7a46760","tid":1465720,"uid":300816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"死都唔割"},{"pid":"c8c2b86314c14f36f4310514c0f4e97cc7a708de","tid":1465720,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"講得好, 前線決定, 好事放大, 錯事齊補鑊"},{"pid":"6be6bd94a4c0fa89ffdf5206f98bddeed516c449","tid":1465720,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited